<div id="review_3524511255" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3524511255" />
    <a title="Boo" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/9333847-boo"><img alt="Boo" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1643663399p2/9333847.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3524511255?book_show_action=true">Sep 12, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Boo" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Boo" href="/user/show/9333847-boo">Boo</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3524511255" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7511027198981727181">3.5⭐️ making my way through reading all the plays I’ve seen performed on stage and finally got to this one.</span>

