      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/12524.James_Goldman">About James Goldman</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/12524.James_Goldman"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1343057581p3/12524.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/12524.James_Goldman">James Goldman
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
19
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer10029912742200774305">James Goldman was an American Academy Award-winning screenwriter and playwright, and the brother of screenwriter and novelist <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/12521.William_Goldman' title='William Goldman' rel='nofollow noopener'>William Goldman</a>.<br/><br/>He was born in Chicago, Illinois and grew up primarily in Highland Park, Illinois, a Chicago suburb. He is most noted as the author of <i>The Lion in Winter</i> and author of the book for the stage musical <i>Follies</i>.<br/><br/>Goldman died from a heart attack in New York City, </span>
  <span id="freeText10029912742200774305" style="display:none">James Goldman was an American Academy Award-winning screenwriter and playwright, and the brother of screenwriter and novelist <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/12521.William_Goldman" title="William Goldman" rel="nofollow noopener">William Goldman</a>.<br /><br />He was born in Chicago, Illinois and grew up primarily in Highland Park, Illinois, a Chicago suburb. He is most noted as the author of <i>The Lion in Winter</i> and author of the book for the stage musical <i>Follies</i>.<br /><br />Goldman died from a heart attack in New York City, where he had lived for many years.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10029912742200774305" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
